### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get current user
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me

###

### Create template
POST http://localhost:3000/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Push Day A",
  "description": "Chest and triceps",
  "isPublic": true,
  "exercises": [
    {
      "exerciseName": "Bench Press",
      "targetSets": 4,
      "targetReps": "6-8"
    },
    {
      "exerciseName": "Incline Dumbbell Press",
      "targetSets": 3,
      "targetReps": "8-10"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get my templates
GET http://localhost:3000/templates/mine

###

### Get public templates
GET http://localhost:3000/templates/public

###

### Clone template
POST http://localhost:3000/templates/1/clone

###

### Start a workout session from a template
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/start/1
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Get my sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/sessions/mine

###

### Get a specific session by id
GET http://localhost:3000/sessions/1

###

### Create a set for a session
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions/1/sets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateExerciseId": 1,
  "order": 1,
  "reps": 8,
  "weight": 100,
  "rpe": 8,
  "rir": 2,
  "notes": "Felt good"
}

###

### Update a set
PATCH http://localhost:3000/sessions/sets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reps": 9,
  "weight": 102.5,
  "notes": "Last set, pushed harder"
}